data.text:
Description

This overlay is made of soft medium weight knit fabric. The bottom skirt flounce is a handkerchief style that creates great flow when worshiping the Living God through movement. This overlay also comes in a children version and an array of colors. Shown with our white unity bell sleeved top and palazzo pants which are sold separately. Our inspiration was:

Psalm 19:7

The law of the Lord is perfect, converting the soul: the testimony of the Lord is sure, making wise the simple.
